          <dd>
                                        <p>
                                              Mary McWilliams, "With Quite Different Eyes: The Norma Jean Calderwood Collection of Islamic Art", <em>Apollo</em>, ed. David Ekserdjian (November 2002), vol. CLVI no. 490, pp. 12-16, p.15, fig.11
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Mary McWilliams, ed., <em>In Harmony: The Norma Jean Calderwood Collection of Islamic Art</em>, exh. cat., Harvard Art Museums (Cambridge, MA, 2013), p. 14, ill.; pp. 88-89, ill.; p. 236, cat. 94, ill.
                             </p>
                                                      <p>
                                              Yuriko Yamanaka, ed., <em>Cultural History of Marvels in the Middle East and Europe</em>, Nagoya University Press (Nagoya, October 19, 2015), Cover illustration; p. 20
                             </p>
                                    </dd>
        
